breakdown <- readRDS(file = params$breakdown) 
performance_data <- readRDS(file = params$performance_data)
```



# Summary {.unnumbered}

The implementation of the new **`r params$product`** pump system for **`r params$project`** shows exceptional financial performance compared to the current pump infrastructure. **`r params$product`** offers convincing economic advantages. The total savings over **`r params$years`** years are **€`r params$total_savings`**. This means a strong **`r params$roi_percent`%** return on investment. The initial investment will be paid back in **`r params$payback_years`** years. The annual CO2 reduction will be **`r format(calc$annual_co2_savings, big.mark = ",")`** kg.


